data.description: One of San Antonio's most loved walking neighborhoods. Very close to all of downtowns most happening places and dining experiences. Step into your urban sanctuary! Discover this meticulously cared-for residence nestled in the sought-after Lavaca neighborhood, boasting a BRAND NEW HVAC system and numerous enhancements. This fully renovated abode comprises three bedrooms and two bathrooms, designed with a split floorplan for optimal privacy. The contemporary kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and seamlessly flows into an expansive living space. All appliances are included for your convenience! Outside, revel in the lush backyard retreat complete with a freshly installed deck offering views of the iconic Tower of the Americas. Accommodate multiple vehicles with ease thanks to the carport and additional parking on the premises. Welcome to your new home sweet home!
